      "content": "hey im type 1 diabetic and i just finished a long run but now im feeling really weird. i feel super shaky and sweaty and kinda lightheaded like im in a fog. i think maybe my sugar is too high because im feeling off. should i just take an extra unit of insulin to bring it down and stabilize?",
