      "content": "i tried to grab my meter but i'm kinda dizzy and wrestling with the cap, it's hard to focus. honestly i usually feel like this when my sugar is high so i just wanna get ahead of it before it gets worse. if i just do 1 or 2 units now it should help right? i dont want to wait and have it spike.",
